name: Interdimensional Friendship: Cat and Butterfly (Blueprint)
description:
One didn't trust the other, one just didn’t care, one was stronger and sharp, one was small, one was fighting for it’s life, one just took it as a playtime, one could fly, one could stand, one could kill the other. 
But, it’s only because of their physical form and that’s how nature works. 
They could meet in a different dimension, they feel safe together, they couldn’t hurt each other, they weren't afraid of dying, they could play together, they could live.
